{"tid":1497623,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我唔明點解一定要聽日8.24 7-11塞機場？","createTime":"2019-08-23T05:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T08:05:47.000Z","uid":299085,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"192e8a1387aa341edad58658370950804563bf85","tid":1497623,"uid":299085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"(呢個已經係機場po出左，但冇回應，或者因為有人狂推幾十頁，根本沉到冇人睇到。)<br />\n<br />\n同意機場係緊要目標，但一直對日期時間有D保留，主要因為驚影響觀塘(個人認c為智能燈柱老早應該煲大佢)。<br />\n<br />\n爬左幾個po，揾到有巴打話時間上選擇係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為就貨運最繁忙時間</strong></span>。咁我明星期六去係合理，但好似tg 定邊到有人話<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>貨運上午唔係最忙</strong></span>，但追唔到有冇回覆。如果有，請分享。<br />\n<br />\n於是我自己 Google, 揾到機場 link <a href=\"https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/departures/cargo.page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongairport.com%2Ftc%2Fflights%2Fdepartures%2Fcargo.page&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1RV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=63c608d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongairport.com/tc/flights/departures/cargo.page</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8.24 貨運離港班機</strong></span><br />\n0000-0600 33 班機<br />\n0600 -1200 21 班機<br />\n1200 - 1800 16 班機<br />\n1800 - 0000 24 班機<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8.24 貨運抵港班機</strong></span><br />\n0000-0600 34 班機<br />\n0600 -1200 21 班機<br />\n1200 - 1800 17 班機<br />\n1800 - 0000 22 班機<br />\n<br />\n咁我想問，似乎7-11 呢個唔係 block 到最多貨運。係未我睇錯，定有其他原因要8.24 7-11呢個時間最好呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申 好驚觀塘唔够人，或者「和你塞」如果有小小唔理想嘅場面，就有機會令觀塘，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>尤其是燈柱問題</strong></span>，被失蹤。"},{"pid":"639c2268763bcf32fb46f91303e79f55975e6d86","tid":1497623,"uid":299085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"e71022e502331fdf94ee22dcf850d22a41b7f799","tid":1497623,"uid":299085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:01:15.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a6daf40ac06091af